<item>
            <title>[SOLR-5127] Allow multiple wildcards in hl.fl</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-5127</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a wildcard is present in the hl.fl field, the field is not split up at commas/spaces into components. As a consequence settings like hl.fl=&lt;b&gt;_highlight,&lt;/b&gt;_data do not work.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Splitting the string first and evaluating wildcards on each component afterwards would be more powerful and consistent with the documentation.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12662830">SOLR-5127</key>
            <summary>Allow multiple wildcards in hl.fl</summary>
